{"tid":1061813,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"比著你，你會唔會遮果個女仔？","createTime":"2019-03-14T16:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T10:30:39.000Z","uid":189386,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1fc5f402888eebbd1a826fd30e7f68ffe372a0a0","tid":1061813,"uid":189386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T16:00:52.000Z","msg":"假設落緊雨，唔細雨，但又唔係好大<br />\n<br />\n你等緊過馬路，格離有個女仔冇帶遮，有點狼狽<br />\n<br />\n你會唔會遮埋佢？<br />\n<br />\n但其實仲有其他人都係冇但遮等緊過路，佢地可能都會怨你淨係遮個女仔，又會令個女仔諗：做乜咁多人唔幫淨係幫我，會唔會有企圖？<br />\n<br />\n我試過有次，我行埋左一步諗住遮佢啦，但太怕羞冇出聲問<br />\n<br />\n佢一見我行埋黎，即刻彈開左一步，寧願dup乳都唔比我遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n只此留下左永不 磨滅嘅陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a318942811615542a24791d2fdd0caaab961ab","tid":1061813,"uid":58140,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T16:03:48.000Z","msg":"你的樣子如何"},{"pid":"4c2ea533768d67d1b00f2ec3c0b5c3e652c70745","tid":1061813,"uid":21423,"like":6,"dislike":24,"score":-18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T16:04:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d783841a0a306b1bc684eba75ea50a3b1dedca35","tid":1061813,"uid":189386,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"4c2ea533768d67d1b00f2ec3c0b5c3e652c70745","tid":1061813,"uid":21423,"like":6,"dislike":24,"score":-18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T16:04:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T16:07:11.000Z","msg":"好似有得賣<br />\n利申：做果欄"},{"pid":"e889b80b756d2ea9f3cb20b86d9cc3424bb19893","tid":1061813,"uid":189386,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"91a318942811615542a24791d2fdd0caaab961ab","tid":1061813,"uid":58140,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T16:03:48.000Z","msg":"你的樣子如何"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T16:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c7f22f62e3c1e137c24d3cc9518c0433c41964","tid":1061813,"uid":22756,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T16:07:39.000Z","msg":"臭雞港女永遠都係立壞心腸睇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根本睇樣"},{"pid":"7508bf2ac96ef4d6d4c630214ba6b1b23ba2e2ef","tid":1061813,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T16:08:38.000Z","msg":"通常遮男人先"},{"pid":"ee737553116530732b681f5688910b2257a229ed","tid":1061813,"uid":189386,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"7508bf2ac96ef4d6d4c630214ba6b1b23ba2e2ef","tid":1061813,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T16:08:38.000Z","msg":"通常遮男人先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T16:09:53.000Z","msg":"個男心諗：有靚女你都唔遮，係咪基架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5ac5795f5da5ad6cad9fe502d36ee1fd19675cf","tid":1061813,"uid":189386,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"40c7f22f62e3c1e137c24d3cc9518c0433c41964","tid":1061813,"uid":22756,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T16:07:39.000Z","msg":"臭雞港女永遠都係立壞心腸睇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根本睇樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T16:10:36.000Z","msg":"咁其實我地都係既<br />\n有豬扒我都唔想遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80303ca406d3c79c95c66124af9d24bc7fed5e9","tid":1061813,"uid":22830,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T16:11:22.000Z","msg":"啱先突然好大雨 <br />\n個個路人有遮 望住我 但無人想遮我<br />\n最後越落越大 結果跑<br />\n做好心唔係必然<br />\n但一個小小嘅動作 <br />\n會令人覺得好窩心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88045da5310fb8440fc425e47cd0bef9dda3d11b","tid":1061813,"uid":227539,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T16:13:19.000Z","msg":"會 因為我都比女仔遮過 所以之後都會遮人"},{"pid